snippet.title: Hyper Rails Loch Ness Monster's Revenge Rollercoaster (POV)
snippet.description:
Please help support The Kurt's Place Channel by visiting my online store at:
https://www.zazzle.com/store/tkpc_online_store

Thank you for stopping by and visiting The Kurt's Place Channel here on YouTube.
I try to upload at least 2 videos each week and sometimes more when my time allows me too.
Videos to see range from Las Vegas attractions to Work Shop videos and many more as well.
Please Subscribe,Like,and Comment during your visit here.
Hope you have a nice day and come back soon.

Thank You Once Again From:
The Kurt's Place Channel
